其是我姐和姐夫，姐姐刚毕业不久，找到一份好工作，姐夫白手起家，处于创业初期，要是这次倾其所有，他们俩很有可能以后就翻不了身了，一直过着还债的生活；不治，老爹可能只有半年到一年的时间，他想让我读研，等我考试研究生的时候，他可能已经不在了，我怕现在不治我会后悔一辈子。 现在商量过后他们就说，决定权在我手上，我说要治，不管怎样他们全力配合我；我说不治，那就用剩下的这段时间带老爹好好出去玩玩，看看风景，再给他点时间见见想见的人，说说想说的话。 社会就是这么冷酷，现实就是如此残酷。老爹老妈勤勤恳恳忙活一辈子，明事理，分是非，待人友善，上天却没能给他们多一点时间来享受哪怕一年清福。作为儿女，什么都做不了，实在惭愧，痛苦万分。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2c3735cebb95fc1c2f82d986ce9c497b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "103 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/446433748"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8rSk3+WM9sRtEAMaCDYxNDg2MjQ1IM+R4YEGMEE44R1AF3IJNDQ2NDMzNzQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1617624662.9000022", "card_id": "Q_47597895", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "程序员需要达到什么水平才能顺利拿到 20k 无压力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作为一个刚入行不久的程序员，如何才能顺利的找一份 20K 的工作？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d917fb11613b7b13ecd7bbeb1c554e6_qhd.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/47597895"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8rSk3+WM9sRtEAMaCDExMjU0MTkzIJK+mbsFMAA4rgNAGHIINDc1OTc4OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1617624662.9003959", "card_id": "Q_322778102", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 253}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么甜甜的睡前小故事吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就是听完会很甜的，洋溢微笑的那种"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-294abb0ced28177d741dde80e4e20027_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/322778102"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8rSk3+WM9sRtEAMaCDM0MDA0NzA0IKyFseYFMAA4hC